message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this exceptional product. I believe it's a great fit for your needs. You can have it for $25000.
Alice, I appreciate your offer, but $25000 is way above my budget. I'm prepared to make a fair offer at $8000. Let's work together to reach an agreement that reflects both our interests.

Thank you for your offer, Bob. I understand budget constraints, but given the value and quality of the product, I can offer it to you for $20000. I believe this is a fair compromise that meets both our interests.
